                                </div>
                                <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
                                    <a href="/odr/standards/code-of-ethics" class="bn-standards-hub-card"><strong>Code of ethics — neutrals</strong><span>Impartiality &amp; fees</span></a>
                                </div>
                                <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
                                    <a href="/odr/standards/hearing-protocol" class="bn-standards-hub-card"><strong>Hearing &amp; submissions</strong><span>Written rounds → virtual hearing</span></a>
                                </div>
                                <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
                                    <a href="/odr/standards/neutral-appointment" class="bn-standards-hub-card"><strong>Neutral appointment</strong><span>Vetting &amp; challenges</span></a>
                                </div>
                                <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
                                    <a href="/odr/standards/empanelment" class="bn-standards-hub-card"><strong>Empanelment rules</strong><span>Panel governance</span></a>
                                </div>
